pan&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;йқһжқғеЁҒеә”зӯ”:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;еҗҚз§°:    &lt;span class=&#34;selector-tag&#34;&gt;label&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;selector-class&#34;&gt;.dolphin-ai&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;selector-class&#34;&gt;.cn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Addresses:  &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;2606&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;4700&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;3030&lt;/span&gt;::ac43:a188&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;          &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;2606&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;4700&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;3032&lt;/span&gt;::&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;6815&lt;/span&gt;:f2a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;          &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;104.21&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;15.42&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;          &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;172.67&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;161.136&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;жҲ–иҖ…еҲ·ж–°жң¬ең° DNS (дёҚиҝҮдёҖиҲ¬ж— ж•Ҳ, йҷӨйқһй…ҚзҪ®дәҶдёҠжёё DNS жҳҜ 8.8.8.8 д№Ӣзұ»зҡ„, дёҚз„¶иҝҗиҗҘе•Ҷзҡ„д№ҹжҳҜең°еҹҹжҖ§зҡ„жІЎеҲ·ж–°)&lt;/p&gt;
